Package: measures
Title: Performance Measures for Statistical Learning
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Philipp", "Probst", email = "philipp_probst@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides the biggest amount of statistical measures in the whole R world. Includes measures of regression, (multiclass) classification, clustering, survival and multilabel classification. The measures come mainly from the 'mlr' package and were programed by several 'mlr' developers. 
Depends: R (>= 3.0),
         stats
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
